{
  "text": "Obviously we would very much like to not get to the point of surgery, and the only other alternative that comes to mind other than the diet and the instrument's personal mental work is healing through a healer, and I would like Ra's recommendation with respect to a non-allopathic type healer and any recommendations Ra could make for either Jim or myself to act in that capacity or anyone else Ra could recommend so that we wouldn't have to go through this surgical operation if it seems to become necessary and if we could start working on one of these other approaches right away I think it might be highly recommended. Would Ra comment on that, please? I am Ra. We salute the opening of compassion circuitry in the questioner but note that that which is being experienced by this group is being experienced within an healing atmosphere. The healing hands of each have limited use when the distortion has so many metaphysical layers and mixtures. Therefore, look not to a healing but to the joy of companionship, for each is strong and has its feet set upon the way. The moon casts its shadows. What shall you see? Link hands and walk towards the sun. In this instance this is the greatest healing. For the physical vehicle we can suggest far less than you had hoped.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Obviously we would very much like to not get to the point of surgery, and the only other alternative that comes to mind other than the diet and the instrument's personal mental work is healing through a healer, and I would like Ra's recommendation with respect to a non-allopathic type healer and any recommendations Ra could make for either Jim or myself to act in that capacity or anyone else Ra could recommend so that we wouldn't have to go through this surgical operation if it seems to become necessary and if we could start working on one of these other approaches right away I think it might be highly recommended.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 622,
        "start": 3.24,
        "end": 84.002
      },
      {
        "segment": "Would Ra comment on that, please?",
        "start_offset": 623,
        "end_offset": 656,
        "start": 84.042,
        "end": 97.423
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 657,
        "end_offset": 665,
        "start": 97.523,
        "end": 97.663
      },
      {
        "segment": "We salute the opening of compassion circuitry in the questioner but note that that which is being experienced by this group is being experienced within an healing atmosphere.",
        "start_offset": 666,
        "end_offset": 840,
        "start": 97.683,
        "end": 158.784
      },
      {
        "segment": "The healing hands of each have limited use when the distortion has so many metaphysical layers and mixtures.",
        "start_offset": 841,
        "end_offset": 949,
        "start": 163.664,
        "end": 208.266
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, look not to a healing but to the joy of companionship, for each is strong and has its feet set upon the way.",
        "start_offset": 950,
        "end_offset": 1069,
        "start": 211.546,
        "end": 259.567
      },
      {
        "segment": "The moon casts its shadows.",
        "start_offset": 1070,
        "end_offset": 1097,
        "start": 262.687,
        "end": 270.287
      },
      {
        "segment": "What shall you see?",
        "start_offset": 1098,
        "end_offset": 1117,
        "start": 272.767,
        "end": 277.788
      },
      {
        "segment": "Link hands and walk towards the sun.",
        "start_offset": 1118,
        "end_offset": 1154,
        "start": 281.088,
        "end": 294.388
      },
      {
        "segment": "In this instance this is the greatest healing.",
        "start_offset": 1155,
        "end_offset": 1201,
        "start": 298.748,
        "end": 310.908
      },
      {
        "segment": "For the physical vehicle we can suggest far less than you had hoped.",
        "start_offset": 1202,
        "end_offset": 1270,
        "start": 314.248,
        "end": 338.249
      }
    ],
